{"id": "1412857053671850156", "channel_id": "1412857053671850156", "type": 0, "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "author_bot": false, "content": "The power up version of the Embryo card produced by Thais has a strange wording: \"Can be Devour and trigger 2 effects\"\nI think it should be changed in to: \"Can be consumed to trigger the Devour effect 2 times\" or something on those lines to make the effect more clear.", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T17:49:31.210000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-03T17:50:17.400000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1412857054317514842", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 150219, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412857053671850156/1412857054317514842/image.png?ex=69cc092b&is=69cab7ab&hm=3f25d8bebffe594f52a50d4cf1d3c8f298e26bc557f09edf827d5906fccebec3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412857053671850156", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Scion of Purity wording", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1412737241012375624", "channel_id": "1412737241012375624", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "So, in the lineups, when you have a team with a character that has a covenant, and you switch to another team with the same character at the same spot but normally no covenants, then the covenant will still appear on the other team.\nAnd vice-versa, if you go from a team that the character has no covenant to a team where that character has a covenant, it will show it doesn't have a covenant.\n\nFurther testing led me to notice that in fact it also happens with 2 different covenants, as long as the same character is on the same spot in the team, changing team will visually override the covenant on the other team.\n\nThis doesn't happen if the character is not on the same spot in the team however.\n\nAs shown in the video, pay attention to Thais's Covenant.", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T09:53:25.646000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1412737242115473468", "filename": "2025-09-03_11-47-20.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 14076297, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1412737241012375624/1412737242115473468/2025-09-03_11-47-20.mp4?ex=69cc4255&is=69caf0d5&hm=13352368fc38128dbb0f0be626dbdcb16330c4e87e750aee4b0d2194c8128d87&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412737241012375624", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Covenants visually misleading in lineups", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
