{"id": "1412833800764919929", "channel_id": "1412833800764919929", "type": 0, "author_id": "478214049033879563", "author_name": "yannic2112", "author_bot": false, "content": "The magical hat randomly changes the arithmetica cost of most cards that you draw (an exclusion is for example Jenkin' ult). The cards glow yellow for reduced/ same arithmetica cost and red for increased arithmetica cost compared to the cards original cost. This however blocks any visual clues that you normally get for card abilities. I have not seen a case where those colours from the Hat actually help, it just makes it more difficult to navigate your hand, especially since it is not uncommon to hold 10+ cards, on top of the Hat also making you draw 2 additional cards at the start of the turn.\nI suggest either completely removing the visual clue from the had, or making it so that the visual clue comes in a different form, like the number itself on the card being yellow/ red to indicate the change in cost or there being a little upwards-pointing yellow arrow/ downwards-pointing red arrow next to the number of each cards arithmetica cost.", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T16:17:07.285000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412833800764919929", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Change visual effect of Trickster's Hat", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1412835314657136742", "channel_id": "1412833800764919929", "type": 0, "author_id": "233874560682950656", "author_name": "wolfierce", "author_bot": false, "content": "I concur for the numbers being colored if higher or lower cost than original instead of the whole card", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T16:23:08.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412833800764919929", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Change visual effect of Trickster's Hat", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1412817837487292488", "channel_id": "1412817837487292488", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "To easily drop the burden of daily dive, could you please remove the relic bonus to the final score?\n\nI would love it if I didn't have to get my relic bar full to get a high score and I could just skip ahead to the boss and noticed fight most of the battles.\n\nSo if I only have 1 relic, my score isn't lower than someone with 8 relics.\n\nYou can check my account and see that I've been missing completing these dailies as they just take to long with some event tasks too.", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T15:13:41.343000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1412817837487292488", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Lessen Burden - Daily Dive", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
